EASTERN CARIBBEAN SEA.
MARTINIQUE TO SAINT LUCIA.
SEVEN METER M/V FAMILY'S BOAT, WHITE HULL, SIX PERSONS
ON BOARD, OVERDUE FORT DE FRANCE (14-36N 061-05W) TO

ASSIST IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO MRCC FORT DE FRANCE,
